      "title": "Sign up corn farmers to buy urea",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, farmers have been given the opportunity to register through the www.agrarian.lk website to provide urea fertilizer for maize cultivation during the high season.",
        "The Ministry of Agriculture said that arrangements have been made to provide the 50 kg bundle of urea fertilizer which was given to the farmers at the price of 10,000 rupees, to the maize farmers at the same price."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
